Name: NaziShootout
About the game: GamePlay: Buy guns and ammo with gold. Kill nazis in town and try to survive as long as possible. Features: • FPS: NaziShootout is a first person shooter • Guns: LugerP08, Thompson, Sten, Welrod, and more! • Survive: Survive as long as possible in town from nazis • $Gold: Used to purchase guns and ammo in town • HardCore: No save/load, no hp or armor ui, and no checkpoints • KillCount: Keep track of nazis killed
